cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

The paper deals with neural networks and their capacity to absorb information, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also applies the proposed Sparsely-Gated Mixture-of-Experts layer to language modeling and machine translation tasks, which are subfields of natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also addresses algorithmic and performance challenges, which are relevant to the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV).
